{"tid":177113,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[好困擾] 尋晚去飲，撞返個以前一齊玩嘅女仔","createTime":"2017-03-28T15:34:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T04:41:40.000Z","uid":100347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b26861b18e87cdd8b80abf0841c311f14fd9b0ff","tid":177113,"uid":100347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T15:34:31.000Z","msg":"第一次開post, 如果睇到一舊雲，講聲唔好意思先<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n興趣班嘅一個前輩結婚，咁新朗有個侄女以前都有學過一排，細個果陣我同個女仔幾乎堂堂都玩埋一齊， 甚至堂堂都被新朗罵，太曳。後來大家都無再學。<br />\n                                     <br />\n見返先記得原來有時搭地鐵都撞到呢個人，但只覺得對眼好熟。唔記得佢，個女仔亦唔記得我。<br />\n<br />\n等開席果陣叫埋佢嚟打麻雀，都係吹下水，咁有另一條友以前同個女仔唔熟嘅唔識嘅，就自告奮勇去教佢，所以個女仔都算識打。臨開席埋位我就同個女仔交換電話facebook，諗住十幾年無見 識返佢咁。                <br />\n<br />\n點知成班人起曬哄，被佢地話抄牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />果陣都幾尷尬，係嘈到連主人家甚至最遠張枱都有人都望過嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n埋位果陣有好幾條友都叫我去同個女仔坐嘅，不過我又無咁嘅打算。最後坐另一張枱<br />\n(反而教打牌個男仔神咁早走去坐佢旁邊)<br />\n<br />\n成餐飯間中都有搵下個女仔嘅，但佢旁邊果位新朋友全程R水吹，見我過來 個語氣就一直好似好想趕我走咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n頭先帶頭起哄㗎，最後見到佢靜雞雞抄人牌，走果陣全程whatsapp<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n位仁兄唔知有意無意，好proud咁講：<br />\n<em>我連佢電話啊facebook啊連住邊返咩工都知啦！</em><br />\n<br />\n其實好多人都知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n純粹諗住識返以前啲人，但我係咪踩親人條尾？<br />\n<br />\n宜家就好驚個女仔同佢屋企人亂諗野，印象中 好多是非精亂講野<br />\n<br />\n如果你係我，會點拆？<br />\n如果妳係個女仔，見到個新認識嘅人被人咁玩法，會唔會對佢有戒心？"},{"pid":"906f1073f44580b0cf571863a8c69f59b8d4651a","tid":177113,"uid":2515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T15:39:53.000Z","msg":"渣ga 驚呢樣驚果樣<br />\n<br />\n人地女都溝撚埋你先慢慢介意呢樣果樣啦下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30041bd268e56f26c8714394ed6d80a19b2ab035","tid":177113,"uid":100347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T15:54:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>渣ga 驚呢樣驚果樣<br />\n<br />\n人地女都溝撚埋你先慢慢介意呢樣果樣啦下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n打算同佢做個朋友咋，女仔朋友唔多<br />\n但班人 就覺得我想追人咁<br />\n<br />\n反而真係想"},{"pid":"fe17bb51f285b6ae2e28b09f66b8b43ba28d9a1d","tid":177113,"uid":100347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T15:55:26.000Z","msg":"反而真係想知如果係你地 會點睇"},{"pid":"fcbaf0e85267403c828ab1b8fd1b86784381523a","tid":177113,"uid":100347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T16:04:15.000Z","msg":"Can someone help me<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65a4c872ea999096b90d16fcee33530111c4af25","tid":177113,"uid":100347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T20:47:03.000Z","msg":"已酒醒 <br />\n<br />\n其實無咩大不了，此po已完"},{"pid":"c4c08ca858603e5904d14cce0b28770fbfb15808","tid":177113,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T20:51:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>已酒醒 <br />\n<br />\n其實無咩大不了，此po已完</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n感情台係時候轉名為「醉酒台」"},{"pid":"804e5e16c259a74c3cef6268c649a7fbddb9edaa","tid":177113,"uid":75445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T23:40:09.000Z","msg":"驚呢樣驚過樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a26ae2608f96c5b8b53a28eb4968b59844186faf","tid":177113,"uid":30751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T23:42:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>已酒醒 <br />\n<br />\n其實無咩大不了，此po已完</blockquote><br />\n飲醉左打字都算有文有路喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6bffa1b96eeae7e69be8498f57aef1e8897067a","tid":177113,"uid":16978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T23:54:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>已酒醒 <br />\n<br />\n其實無咩大不了，此po已完</blockquote><br />\n飲醉左打字都算有文有路喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n飲醉左 = 驚<br />\n酒醒 = 驚乜撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69c17a06b87c2a2c4a26cb0ce818e9a648a79b87","tid":177113,"uid":6964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T04:41:40.000Z","msg":"心動不行動 機會流失了"}]}